cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY. 

The paper combines deep learning and classical planning, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. The use of deep learning and neural architectures for action modeling and state representation suggests that it could belong to cs.AI and cs.LG. The use of image-based versions of planning domains suggests that it could belong to cs.CV. The use of Latent Space and the evaluation of the approach on planning domains suggests that it could belong to cs.RO and cs.SY.
